 -----
 Marinade to test :

https://fr.bakeitwithlove.com/curry-chicken-marinade/ :

yogourt grec 150ml
4 tsp jus de citron vert
1 Tbsp poudre de curry
1/2 tsp sel
450g poulet en des

laisser mariner au frigo pendant 4 heures
--
Cuire à la plancha 200C si huile olive
	220C si huile vegetale

	Try 150C

Next thing to try:
	add enough olive oil to plancha, so that it combats citron acidity

I think poulet coupé en dés (grand dés) might be better : No 
whole poulet only.
	prend filet de poulet + applati (pas tranches)
	
---
Final marinade for 1kg thighs

Curing/brining : (is this step necessary ?)
	pulco + plenty of salt and rest for 2-3 minutes
	wash
	let dry
	* If this step is done reduce salt to 0.8 and pulco to 3 tsp
	Let's not do it and see results

preparation : 
	Remove skin
	remove bones
	cut into pieces

Marinade :
	yogourt grec 150g
	4 tsp pulco
	1.5 Tbsp X
		paprika or curry or ..
	1 tsp sel

Conservation :
	Can be consumer after atleast one night of marination
	half put in fridge (max : day after + 2 other days)
		then freeze remaining.
	other half freezing bag
		or freeze both if you want

----------------------
new marinade :
	3 tbsp neutral oil
	4 tsp pulco
	1.5 Tbsp X
		paprika or curry or ..
	1 tsp sel
